Package: scabmnkd
Type: Package
Title: SC-ABM-NKD: Hierarchical Count-Based Spatio-Temporal ABM with Neural Dispersal Kernel
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the SC-ABM-NKD model for spatio-temporal population
    dynamics. Combines a count-based agent-based model (latent NegBin state) with
    a neural dispersal kernel (3-layer ReLU MLP), density-regulated survival,
    Poisson-superposition immigration, long-distance dispersal, and a doubly-
    stochastic observation model (NegBin counts + Bernoulli remote sensing).
    Inference is performed via ABC-SMC with adaptive tolerance. Synthesises
    Hooten & Wikle (2010, JASA), Heard (2014, Duke PhD), and extensions.
